#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid ""
"10:00 AM - 11:00 AM: Case Study Breakdowns: Success Stories &amp; Lessons "
"Learned"
msgstr ""
"10:00 AM - 11:00 AM: ວິເຄາະກໍລະນີສຶກສາ: ເລື່ອງລາວຄວາມສຳເລັດ &amp; ບົດຮຽນທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid ""
"10:15 AM - 11:00 AM: Industry-Specific Data Presentation: \"What Your "
"Customers Really Want\""
msgstr ""
"10:15 AM - 11:00 AM: ການນຳສະເໜີຂໍ້ມູນສະເພາະດ້ານອຸດສາຫະກຳ: \"ສິ່ງທີ່ລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງການແທ້"
"ໆ\""

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"10:30 AM - 11:30 AM: Finding Your Perfect Match: Influencer Identification "
"Workshop"
msgstr ""
"10:30 AM - 11:30 AM: ຄົ້ນຫາຄູ່ຮ່ວມງານທີ່ເໝາະສົມ: ກອງປະຊຸມປະຕິບັດຕົວຈິງໃນການຄັດເລືອກອິນຟລູເອນເຊີ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "11:00 AM - 11:15 AM: Quick Break"
msgstr "11:00 AM - 11:15 AM: ພັກໄລຍະສັ້ນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid "11:00 AM - 11:15 AM: Refreshment Break"
msgstr "11:00 AM - 11:15 AM: ພັກດື່ມນ້ຳ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid ""
"11:15 AM - 12:15 PM: Interactive Session: \"Applying Trends to Your "
"Business\" (Small Group Exercises)"
msgstr ""
"11:15 AM - 12:15 PM: ຊ່ວງສົນທະນາ: \"ການນຳໃຊ້ແນວໂນ້ມເຂົ້າໃນທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ\" (ຝຶກຫັດກຸ່ມຍ່ອຍ)"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid ""
"11:15 AM - 12:30 PM: Live Audit Session: Real-time Analysis of Participant "
"Accounts"
msgstr ""
"11:15 AM - 12:30 PM: ຊ່ວງກວດສອບສົດ: ການວິເຄາະບັນຊີຂອງຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມແບບທັນການ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid "11:30 AM - 11:45 AM: Refreshment Break"
msgstr "11:30 AM - 11:45 AM: ພັກດື່ມນ້ຳ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"11:45 AM - 12:45 PM: From Outreach to Partnership: Building Authentic "
"Relationships"
msgstr ""
"11:45 AM - 12:45 PM: ຈາກການເຂົ້າຫາສູ່ການເປັນຄູ່ຮ່ວມງານ: ການສ້າງຄວາມສຳພັນທີ່ແທ້ຈິງ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid "12:15 PM - 1:00 PM: Networking Lunch"
msgstr "12:15 PM - 1:00 PM: ອາຫານທ່ຽງເພື່ອສ້າງເຄືອຂ່າຍ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "12:30 PM - 1:15 PM: Working Lunch &amp; Problem-Solving Roundtables"
msgstr "12:30 PM - 1:15 PM: ອາຫານທ່ຽງເຮັດວຽກ &amp; ສົນທະນາແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid "12:45 PM - 1:45 PM: Networking Lunch with Guest Creator Panel"
msgstr "12:45 PM - 1:45 PM: ອາຫານທ່ຽງສ້າງເຄືອຂ່າຍກັບທີມງານນັກສ້າງສັນຮັບເຊີນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid ""
"1:00 PM - 2:00 PM: Expert Panel: \"Future-Proofing Your Marketing Strategy\""
msgstr ""
"1:00 PM - 2:00 PM: ເວທີຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານ: \"ການວາງແຜນຍຸດທະສາດການຕະຫຼາດສູ່ອະນາຄົດ\""

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "1:15 PM - 2:30 PM: Hands-on Workshop: Implementing Advanced Techniques"
msgstr "1:15 PM - 2:30 PM: ກອງປະຊຸມປະຕິບັດຕົວຈິງ: ການນຳໃຊ້ເຕັກນິກຂັ້ນສູງ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"1:45 PM - 3:00 PM: Campaign Architecture: Briefing, Content Strategy &amp; "
"Creative Freedom"
msgstr ""
"1:45 PM - 3:00 PM: ໂຄງສ້າງແຄມເປນ: ການບຣີຟງານ, ຍຸດທະສາດເນື້ອຫາ &amp; ອິດສະຫຼະໃນການສ້າງ"
"ສັນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid "2:00 PM - 2:45 PM: Personalized Strategy Building Workshop"
msgstr "2:00 PM - 2:45 PM: ກອງປະຊຸມສ້າງຍຸດທະສາດສະເພາະບຸກຄົນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid ""
"2:30 PM - 3:30 PM: Strategy Development: Creating Your 90-Day Action Plan"
msgstr "2:30 PM - 3:30 PM: ການພັດທະນາຍຸດທະສາດ: ສ້າງແຜນປະຕິບັດງານ 90 ວັນຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid "2:45 PM - 3:00 PM: Closing Remarks &amp; Next Steps"
msgstr "2:45 PM - 3:00 PM: ກ່າວປິດງານ &amp; ຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:sale.order.template,note:marketing_agency.sale_order_template_4
msgid "30 days of post-launch technical support"
msgstr "ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອດ້ານເຕັກນິກ 30 ວັນຫຼັງຈາກເປີດຕົວ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid "3:00 PM - 3:15 PM: Afternoon Break"
msgstr "3:00 PM - 3:15 PM: ພັກບ່າຍ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid "3:00 PM - 3:30 PM: Arrival &amp; Executive Networking"
msgstr "3:00 PM - 3:30 PM: ການມາເຖິງ &amp; ການສ້າງເຄືອຂ່າຍລະດັບບໍລິຫານ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"3:15 PM - 4:15 PM: Advanced Measurement: Tracking Influence Throughout the "
"Funnel"
msgstr "3:15 PM - 4:15 PM: ການວັດແທກຂັ້ນສູງ: ການຕິດຕາມອິດທິພົນຕະຫຼອດຂະບວນການຂາຍ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "3:30 PM - 4:00 PM: Implementation Resources &amp; Tools Review"
msgstr "3:30 PM - 4:00 PM: ການກວດກາຊັບພະຍາກອນ &amp; ເຄື່ອງມືໃນການຈັດຕັ້ງປະຕິບັດ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid "3:30 PM - 4:00 PM: Results Overview: The Quarter in Numbers"
msgstr "3:30 PM - 4:00 PM: ພາບລວມຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ: ຕົວເລກໃນໄຕມາດນີ້"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "4:00 PM - 4:30 PM: Q&amp;A and Personalized Consultations"
msgstr "4:00 PM - 4:30 PM: ຊ່ວງຖາມ-ຕອບ ແລະ ການໃຫ້ຄຳປຶກສາສະເພາະບຸກຄົນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid "4:00 PM - 4:45 PM: Campaign Spotlight: Behind the Success Stories"
msgstr "4:00 PM - 4:45 PM: ຈຸດເດັ່ນຂອງແຄມເປນ: ເບື້ອງຫຼັງເລື່ອງລາວຄວາມສຳເລັດ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"4:15 PM - 5:00 PM: Legal Landscape: Contracts, Disclosures &amp; Compliance"
msgstr ""
"4:15 PM - 5:00 PM: ດ້ານກົດໝາຍ: ສັນຍາ, ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນ &amp; ການປະຕິບັດຕາມລະບຽບ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid ""
"4:45 PM - 5:15 PM: Market Analysis: Competitive Landscape &amp; "
"Opportunities"
msgstr "4:45 PM - 5:15 PM: ການວິເຄາະຕະຫຼາດ: ສະພາບການແຂ່ງຂັນ &amp; ໂອກາດ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid "5:00 PM - 5:30 PM: Implementation Planning &amp; Resource Sharing"
msgstr ""
"5:00 PM - 5:30 PM: ການວາງແຜນການຈັດຕັ້ງປະຕິບັດ &amp; ການແບ່ງປັນຊັບພະຍາກອນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid ""
"5:15 PM - 6:00 PM: Strategic Planning Workshop: Setting Next Quarter "
"Priorities"
msgstr "5:15 PM - 6:00 PM: ກອງປະຊຸມວາງແຜນຍຸດທະສາດ: ການກຳນົດບຸລິມະສິດໃນໄຕມາດໜ້າ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid ""
"6:00 PM - 7:30 PM: Celebration Reception with Craft Cocktails &amp; Premium "
"Networking"
msgstr ""
"6:00 PM - 7:30 PM: ງານລ້ຽງສະຫຼອງດ້ວຍຄັອກເທວ ແລະ ການສ້າງເຄືອຂ່າຍລະດັບພຣີມຽມ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid "8:30 AM - 9:00 AM: Check-in &amp; Digital Assessment Setup"
msgstr "8:30 AM - 9:00 AM: ລົງທະບຽນ &amp; ກຽມການປະເມີນແບບດີຈີຕອນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid ""
"9:00 AM - 10:00 AM: State of the Channel: Latest Trends, Algorithm Changes "
"&amp; Best Practices"
msgstr ""
"9:00 AM - 10:00 AM: ສະຖານະຂອງຊ່ອງທາງ: ແນວໂນ້ມຫຼ້າສຸດ, ການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງອັນກໍຣິທຶມ &amp; ວິທີປ"
"ະຕິບັດທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid "9:00 AM - 9:30 AM: Registration &amp; Networking Breakfast"
msgstr "9:00 AM - 9:30 AM: ລົງທະບຽນ &amp; ອາຫານເຊົ້າສ້າງເຄືອຂ່າຍ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid "9:00 AM - 9:30 AM: Welcome Coffee &amp; Influence Assessment"
msgstr "9:00 AM - 9:30 AM: ກາເຟຕ້ອນຮັບ &amp; ການປະເມີນອິດທິພົນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_1
msgid ""
"9:30 AM - 10:15 AM: Keynote: \"The Shifting Digital Landscape\" by our Chief"
" Strategy Officer"
msgstr ""
"9:30 AM - 10:15 AM: ປາຖະກະຖາ: \"ການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງໂລກດີຈີຕອນ\" ໂດຍ ຫົວໜ້າຝ່າຍຍຸດທະສາດ ຂອງ"
"ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"9:30 AM - 10:30 AM: The Influence Landscape: Trends, Platforms &amp; Creator"
" Economy"
msgstr ""
"9:30 AM - 10:30 AM: ພາບລວມຂອງອິດທິພົນ: ແນວໂນ້ມ, ແພລັດຟອມ &amp; ລະບົບເສດຖະກິດຂອງນັກສ້າງ"
"ສັນ"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_4
msgid ""
"<em>Each client receives a beautifully designed Results Portfolio with "
"comprehensive analytics, campaign highlights, and strategic recommendations "
"to share with your broader team.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>ລູກຄ້າແຕ່ລະທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບແຟ້ມຜົນງານ (Results Portfolio) ທີ່ອອກແບບມາຢ່າງສວຍງາມ ພ້ອມກັບການ"
"ວິເຄາະທີ່ຄົບຖ້ວນ, ຈຸດເດັ່ນຂອງແຄມເປນ ແລະ ຄຳແນະນຳທາງຍຸດທະສາດເພື່ອແບ່ງປັນໃຫ້ກັບທີມງານຂອງທ່ານ.</"
"em>"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_3
msgid ""
"<em>Each participant receives a comprehensive workbook, digital resource "
"toolkit, and 30 days of expert email support following the masterclass.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມແຕ່ລະທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບປຶ້ມແບບຝຶກຫັດທີ່ຄົບຖ້ວນ, ຊຸດເຄື່ອງມືຊັບພະຍາກອນດີຈີຕອນ ແລະ ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອທ"
"າງອີເມວຈາກຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານເປັນເວລາ 30 ວັນ ຫຼັງຈາກຈົບຫ້ອງຮຽນ.</em>"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:event.event,description:marketing_agency.event_event_2
msgid ""
"<em>Limited to 25 attendees to ensure personalized guidance. Early "
"registration recommended as sessions typically reach capacity.</em>"
msgstr ""
