#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:marketing_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to your new Odoo Marketing Agency package! This guide will help you "
"navigate the key features and get your agency operations running "
"efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ແພັກເກດ Odoo Marketing Agency ໃໝ່ຂອງທ່ານ! ຄູ່ມືນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານໃຊ້ງານຟີເຈີຫຼັກ ແລະ ດ"
"ຳເນີນງານເອເຈນຊີໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:marketing_agency.knowledge_tour
