#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:marketing_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your Odoo for Marketing Agencies package includes the essential apps to "
"manage your client relationships, projects, and agency operations:"
msgstr ""
"ແພັກເກດ Odoo ສຳລັບເອເຈນຊີການຕະຫຼາດຂອງທ່ານ ລວມມີແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນໃນການຈັດການຄວາມສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ, ໂ"
"ໂງການ ແລະ ການດຳເນີນງານຂອງເອເຈນຊີ:"

#. module: marketing_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:marketing_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your package includes a \"Website\" quotation template with a built-in quote"
" calculator. Simply check boxes for different website features, and the "
"calculator automatically updates the price. This system can be customized "
"for any service your agency offers, making proposal creation fast and "
"consistent."
msgstr ""
"ແພັກເກດຂອງທ່ານມີແບບຟອມໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ \"Website\" ພ້ອມເຄື່ອງຄິດໄລ່ໃນຕົວ. ພຽງແຕ່ເລືອກຟີເຈີທີ່ຕ້ອງກາ"
"ນ, ລະບົບຈະປັບລາຄາໃຫ້ອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການສ້າງຂໍ້ສະເໜີໄວ ແລະ ເປັນມາດຕະຖານ."

